snippet.textDisplay: Loved the song, I think I heard the song over 100 times on a single day... I had a little difficulty in under standing the lyrics; being a Bengali it was like you are able to understand the words but not able to figure out the exact meaning. So it was a predicament of mine, anyways I finally got the complete lyrics of the song and heard the original one too. Later one is longer; I would have liked you guys to give us the complete song because you guys did an awesome job... Hats off to #RamSampath #SonaMohapatra #RituRaj #Dopeadelicz and all the musicians. Coming to the music, I personally liked the pulsating pad sound from the synthesizer filling the background rhythm apart from the guitar of course... Hats off to you guys. Keep up the good work...Hats off Coke Studio...
